{"tid":2059391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"就讀港大小粉紅：香港被中共同化是「大勢所趨」 不認為應反抗","createTime":"2020-06-11T01:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T06:10:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da064b28edf235e27ac87e0409280fb147a4ec43","tid":2059391,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:31:12.000Z","msg":"大學是反修例風波的其中一個「主戰場」，除了影響本地生，內地生同樣受到衝擊。有在中文大學修業的內地生表示，去年11月發生二號橋衝突後，不少內地生希望撤離，但她反而想留在中大見證事件，她認為，香港情況與內地有密切關連，中央政府收緊對香港控制，亦意味對內地有同樣取態，港區國安法立法後，恐怕香港的自由被削。<br />\n<br />\n至於在港大的另一名內地生就不認同示威者的暴力行為，認為無助爭取訴求，最終受影響的是普羅大眾，香港被內地同化亦是大勢所趨。這兩名內地生同樣猶豫應否繼續留港。8間教資會資助大學表示，今年內地生申請退學的數字同往年相若。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305852&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1305852%26csid%3D261_341&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=b6c2f488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305852&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"d3384648f6a8be16cb85c88cc6f49f1f9f123d59","tid":2059391,"uid":285371,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"被人強姦不應反抗<br />\ngoodest logic"},{"pid":"7fde9927e0c1e82249ebed9efa1fb4c356b770c2","tid":2059391,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你去大灣區讀啦"},{"pid":"969dd874234ac3ee62d477a324606978d63faa85","tid":2059391,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa727a318ed7022d00d88bd993629a7821e42dd","tid":2059391,"uid":152476,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"又要香港既獨特性<br />\n又要香港變中國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" c